Achievements.Name: Valedictorian
Achievements.Description: Prove your mettle at all of the Park City challenges.

Achievements.Name: Baron Von Connors
Achievements.Description: Earn respect from the riders at Park City.

Achievements.Name: Grouchbedoit
Achievements.Description: Earn respect from the riders in Europe.

Achievements.Name: Terrani
Achievements.Description: Prove your mettle at all of the European challenges.

Achievements.Name: Itto-Ryu
Achievements.Description: Prove your mettle at all of the Japan challenges.

Achievements.Name: Musashi
Achievements.Description: Earn respect from the riders in Japan.

Achievements.Name: All Aska
Achievements.Description: Prove your mettle at all of the Alaska challenges.

Achievements.Name: Frequent Flyer

Achievements.Name: Ultimate Ultimate
Achievements.Description: How do you become the ultimate of the Ultimate Competitions?

Achievements.Name: OMG!
Achievements.Description: You can never have enough respect!

Achievements.Name: Supa Powa

Achievements.Name: Dr. Air

Achievements.Name: Dr. Jib
Achievements.Description: You're going to need a pretty big rail for this one.

Achievements.Name: High Stakes

Achievements.Name: Tanaba
Achievements.Description: Up for a lot of friendly competition in Japan?

Achievements.Name: Ice Worm

Achievements.Name: New Kid on the Block

Achievements.Name: Mecha Shredzilla

Achievements.Name: CAPiTA®

Achievements.Name: Bonii
